		"description": "<p>At 10th level as an action, you let out a supernaturally loud roar infused with dragonfear. You can force all creatures of your choice within 60 feet to make a Charisma saving throw against your warlock spell save DC. On a failure they are frightened of you for 1 minute. Frightened creatures may repeat the save at the end of each of their turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. This counts as a dragon's fear ability for the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.spbzig6gpnlcswkw]{Dragon Curse} ability. Once you have used this ability, you cannot do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
